name: Brompton U.S. Cash Flow Kings ETF
longDescription: Brompton U.S. Cash Flow Kings ETF (KNGU) is designed to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Brompton Index One U.S. Cash Flow Kings Index (the Index).
